Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be5}哼 今天也很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be5}我真是让人着迷
